But it has to be started no later than 120 days after the patient has undergone their last bout of immunotherapy - and Kian's finished almost 100 days ago.

Ms Musgrove, who is in the process of booking her flights, said: 'I'm so excited by what has happened, people have just been incredible.

'I want this for Kian so much and I want this to work so badly.

'But I'm also scared. Scared because I'm flying over there alone, not knowing what the future is going to hold.'

